1 Getting started
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1.1 Dependencies
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   Download all dependencies before proceeding to step 1, 
   You will need the following programs:
    - Python (2.5 or higher, 
    but may work on earlier versions of Python)
 
1.2 Starting the Project
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  1. Create local setting. You may take settings_local.py.dist like example or create your own:
echo "
DATABASE_ENGINE = 'postgresql_psycopg2'
DATABASE_NAME = 'my_database'
DATABASE_USER = 'user'
DATABASE_PASSWORD = 'password'
DATABASE_HOST = ''
DATABASE_PORT = '5432'

CACHE_BACKEND = 'dummy:///'
" > ./src/cnprog/local_settings.py
  2. Setup your local smtp server, postfix for example. Or add following lines to local_settings.py to use gmail smtp:
EMAIL_USE_TLS = True
EMAIL_HOST = 'smtp.gmail.com'
EMAIL_HOST_USER = '<gmail account>'
EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD = '<gmail password>'
EMAIL_PORT = 587

  3. python ./bootstrap.py
  4. ./bin/buildout -c
  5. ./bin/instance runserver 8001
